1
00:00:54,926 --> 00:00:55,926
What?

2
00:00:58,046 --> 00:00:59,046
What is this?

3
00:01:01,206 --> 00:01:02,566
Ma'am, what are they saying?

4
00:01:03,064 --> 00:01:04,781
They are saying that
our shop violates the rules.

5
00:01:04,867 --> 00:01:06,867
Drivers are finding it
difficult to pass by our shop.

6
00:01:06,963 --> 00:01:09,776
They are saying many such things.

7
00:01:10,566 --> 00:01:14,886
Just like we feared,
we've lost our shop, Vetri.

8
00:01:15,063 --> 00:01:16,676
Ma'am, sorry.

9
00:01:18,166 --> 00:01:20,543
Leave it, Vetri.
You don't say anything.

10
00:01:20,743 --> 00:01:24,210
We can keep blaming each other.
But, what is the use?

11
00:01:24,486 --> 00:01:27,086
It had to happen
and it has happened.

12
00:01:29,606 --> 00:01:31,846
I should've just
stayed back that day.

13
00:01:32,766 --> 00:01:36,166
But, I went shopping
instead of sending Pandi.

14
00:01:36,910 --> 00:01:39,246
That's why..
Hey, he is coming..

15
00:01:41,886 --> 00:01:44,966
What? How was my magic?

16
00:01:45,646 --> 00:01:46,926
What did we do, sir?

17
00:01:47,676 --> 00:01:49,166
You started the problem, right?

18
00:01:50,366 --> 00:01:53,726
Hey, if you had spoken
like this yesterday,

19
00:01:55,376 --> 00:01:56,766
you wouldn't have lost your shop.

20
00:01:59,943 --> 00:02:02,286
How did you talk to me last night?

21
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:06,000
You thought I'd forget
just because I was drunk.

22
00:02:08,443 --> 00:02:10,526
You even tried to hit me.

23
00:02:11,841 --> 00:02:14,541
Did you think I would just
leave after getting hit?

24
00:02:15,446 --> 00:02:18,286
I will make you beg
on the streets for three months.

25
00:02:21,610 --> 00:02:25,526
Just keep in mind. Yuu shouldn't
have caused trouble with me.

26
00:02:28,486 --> 00:02:31,886
Go and find a way to survive.

27
00:02:32,423 --> 00:02:34,810
Go.
- Sir..

28
00:02:37,876 --> 00:02:40,006
Hey, what do we do now?

29
00:02:40,363 --> 00:02:44,366
House rent, groceries,
my daughter's college fees..

30
00:02:44,723 --> 00:02:47,326
Oh, my God! Just the thought
of it makes my head spin.

31
00:02:51,381 --> 00:02:53,964
Hey, say something.
Don't stand like a statue.

32
00:02:55,326 --> 00:02:58,526
Hey, Vetri, are you
still thinking about that?

33
00:03:00,006 --> 00:03:03,446
If one door closes,
another door will open.

34
00:03:05,406 --> 00:03:08,326
No, ma'am,
I don't mind if I had lost my job.

35
00:03:09,816 --> 00:03:11,096
You lost the business, ma'am.

36
00:03:11,486 --> 00:03:13,686
Hey, what are you saying?

37
00:03:14,112 --> 00:03:17,209
Only after you came
did my business start going well.

38
00:03:17,886 --> 00:03:18,966
Did you forget that?

39
00:03:20,118 --> 00:03:24,678
Every good day is followed
by a bad day. Leave it.

40
00:03:24,846 --> 00:03:25,806
We'll deal with it.

41
00:03:49,243 --> 00:03:50,926
Butcher, I need
200 grams of chicken.

42
00:04:11,753 --> 00:04:12,889
Here is the garnish.

43
00:04:14,589 --> 00:04:16,829
Hey, just keep it and leave.

44
00:04:17,486 --> 00:04:19,566
Looks like you're going to
be here all day, just watching.

45
00:04:20,046 --> 00:04:22,966
Sir, this is not an order list.
This is a cooking guide.

46
00:04:23,246 --> 00:04:25,246
Oh, a cooking guide?
- Yes.

47
00:04:25,453 --> 00:04:26,886
Are you irritating me?

48
00:04:26,953 --> 00:04:30,166
Sir, it wasn't me.
It is from Mr. Ragupathi.

49
00:04:31,731 --> 00:04:35,331
If you try to weasel your way in
by using Mr. Ragupathi's name,

50
00:04:35,443 --> 00:04:36,763
you'll be in big trouble.

51
00:04:36,861 --> 00:04:38,861
Sir, I'm not lying, I swear.

52
00:04:39,614 --> 00:04:42,101
If you don't believe me,
you can call him and ask.

53
00:04:56,756 --> 00:04:59,089
Tell me, Nedumaran.
- Sir.

54
00:05:00,093 --> 00:05:01,933
Sir, they have given me a list

55
00:05:02,293 --> 00:05:05,326
of things like 'karpooravalli',
'adhimadhuram', 'sukku', 'thippili'..

56
00:05:05,676 --> 00:05:08,373
You've given a list of ingredients.
I just wanted to know..

57
00:05:08,610 --> 00:05:11,166
I had sent it.
- Oh.

58
00:05:11,846 --> 00:05:14,343
I just wanted to
cross-check it, sir. That's all.

59
00:05:14,566 --> 00:05:18,126
If I'd known what the issue was,
I'd have made you a herbal drink.

60
00:05:18,366 --> 00:05:20,086
No, nothing serious.

61
00:05:20,310 --> 00:05:24,376
I saw it on the internet and liked
it. That's why I sent you the list.

62
00:05:24,733 --> 00:05:26,610
Okay, sir, definitely.

63
00:05:27,245 --> 00:05:30,078
I will probably try to add some
more wonderful ingredients.

64
00:05:30,210 --> 00:05:32,133
I will send you
a good herbal drink, sir.

65
00:05:32,613 --> 00:05:35,766
Okay, good.
- Take care, sir.

66
00:05:38,010 --> 00:05:38,846
John.

67
00:05:39,943 --> 00:05:43,086
Something is fishy.
Something is wrong.

68
00:05:43,566 --> 00:05:46,366
I don't know what it is.

69
00:05:48,043 --> 00:05:49,726
Anyway, let's see.

70
00:05:50,853 --> 00:05:52,465
Chef, shall we start
the prep for this?

71
00:05:52,513 --> 00:05:55,526
Check the ingredients properly
and start the preparation.

72
00:05:56,206 --> 00:05:57,126
Okay, Chef.

73
00:06:00,193 --> 00:06:01,373
Shiva.
- Yes, Chef.

74
00:06:04,886 --> 00:06:05,723
Chef.

75
00:06:06,184 --> 00:06:07,924
Light the burner
and put it on low flame.

76
00:06:07,973 --> 00:06:11,446
Then place a pan and pour
some water. - Okay, Chef.

77
00:06:21,793 --> 00:06:22,686
Yeah.

78
00:06:28,893 --> 00:06:31,526
Chef.
- Yes, get some turmeric powder.

79
00:06:38,446 --> 00:06:39,686
Correct..

80
00:06:45,073 --> 00:06:47,783
Ask another room service
guy to come. I will give it to him.

81
00:06:48,143 --> 00:06:49,006
Why?

82
00:06:50,246 --> 00:06:53,566
Go, why are you standing here?
Stop glaring and leave.

83
00:06:56,273 --> 00:06:59,966
I'll pluck your eyeballs out
and put them in a soup. Get lost.

84
00:07:20,817 --> 00:07:22,473
Actually, it's a perfect mix, sir.

85
00:07:22,783 --> 00:07:25,486
Measurements and ingredients
are on the correct scale.

86
00:07:25,864 --> 00:07:28,941
You can't find it anywhere on
social media or the internet, sir.

87
00:07:29,163 --> 00:07:31,606
That's Nedumaran's brilliance.
- Thank you, sir.

88
00:07:31,743 --> 00:07:33,843
Ask Vetri to come.
- Okay, sir.

89
00:07:40,603 --> 00:07:41,686
Excuse me, sir.

90
00:07:45,123 --> 00:07:46,046
Sir.

91
00:07:46,968 --> 00:07:48,085
Vetri.
- Tell me, sir.

92
00:07:48,189 --> 00:07:50,639
Check if the ingredients are
correct in this herbal drink.

93
00:07:54,283 --> 00:07:56,783
I'm telling you, just check it.
- Okay, sir.

94
00:08:10,943 --> 00:08:13,086
Sir, he has added
everything correctly.

95
00:08:13,810 --> 00:08:15,806
He has added some extra things.

96
00:08:16,526 --> 00:08:18,206
It will help your cold, sir.

97
00:08:18,743 --> 00:08:20,043
Nedumaran.
- Sir.

98
00:08:20,203 --> 00:08:22,043
Everything you said is correct.
- Okay, sir.

99
00:08:22,203 --> 00:08:23,846
You can't find it on the internet.

100
00:08:24,483 --> 00:08:28,766
Because all the ingredients
in this were listed by Vetri.

101
00:08:29,886 --> 00:08:32,479
If Vetri had asked you,

102
00:08:32,597 --> 00:08:34,182
you wouldn't
have done it in the kitchen.

103
00:08:34,943 --> 00:08:37,406
That's why I asked you to do it.

104
00:08:38,143 --> 00:08:42,646
But, I never thought you would
make it yourself and give it to me.

105
00:08:46,126 --> 00:08:49,406
Sir, the guests are waiting.
I'll take my leave.

106
00:08:51,610 --> 00:08:53,423
Thank you, sir.

107
00:08:57,283 --> 00:08:59,086
Nedumaran.
- Sir. - Are you okay?

108
00:08:59,163 --> 00:09:00,686
Yeah, I am fine, sir.

109
00:09:17,434 --> 00:09:18,770
Not bad at all, Maran.

110
00:09:19,163 --> 00:09:21,603
This herbal drink is very
soothing for the throat.

111
00:09:25,966 --> 00:09:27,366
That's Nedumaran's touch.

112
00:09:32,373 --> 00:09:36,310
Sir, I am getting late
for my dinner prep, yeah.

113
00:09:50,676 --> 00:09:51,726
Shit..

114
00:09:52,286 --> 00:09:54,325
Chef, you asked me to come.
Anything important? - Damn you..

115
00:09:54,471 --> 00:09:56,871
Did you see Mr. Ragupathi?
What did he say?

116
00:09:59,142 --> 00:10:00,182
Did he taste the dish?

117
00:10:00,483 --> 00:10:02,886
I tasted the dish.
It was fantastic, Chef.

118
00:10:08,803 --> 00:10:11,446
S-Sorry, Chef. Any problem?

119
00:10:13,486 --> 00:10:15,166
He is testing my patience.

120
00:10:16,046 --> 00:10:18,486
Who, Chef?
- The room service boy.

121
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,103
You mean Vetri?

122
00:10:21,406 --> 00:10:24,126
Who else is disturbing me other
than him in the room service team?

123
00:10:26,183 --> 00:10:29,646
W-What happened, Chef?
- First, he stole my dish.

124
00:10:30,726 --> 00:10:33,806
After that, he entered my
kitchen without my knowledge.

125
00:10:34,646 --> 00:10:38,126
Now, he has made me cook his dish.
- Wow.

126
00:10:38,503 --> 00:10:41,406
So, the one who made us do
the fantastic dish is our Vetri?

127
00:10:42,383 --> 00:10:44,686
John, will you please
shut your mouth?

128
00:10:45,243 --> 00:10:46,326
Just shut up!

129
00:10:47,323 --> 00:10:48,366
Sorry, Chef.

130
00:10:54,566 --> 00:11:00,006
He is screwing up my peaceful
and happy mind from day one, yes.

131
00:11:00,243 --> 00:11:02,903
Chef, you could have fired
him from day one, right?

132
00:11:03,110 --> 00:11:04,893
It is a stupid decision, John.

133
00:11:06,953 --> 00:11:11,006
Nedumaran will not do it.
I hope you know about it, John.

134
00:11:11,533 --> 00:11:12,643
Yes, Chef.

135
00:11:14,006 --> 00:11:15,886
What shall we do
about him now, Chef?

136
00:11:16,678 --> 00:11:19,598
I will catch him one day
in the kitchen.

137
00:11:20,576 --> 00:11:22,846
I will say that he is nothing
and throw him out, right?

138
00:11:23,810 --> 00:11:27,300
Like that, I will make him
feel that he is fit for nothing.

139
00:11:27,413 --> 00:11:29,726
And he is just shit.

140
00:11:30,025 --> 00:11:32,025
Correct, Chef.
- I will do everything for it.

141
00:11:32,253 --> 00:11:34,233
Okay. Chef.
- I will do everything for it.

142
00:11:34,713 --> 00:11:35,966
Relax, Chef.

143
00:11:36,553 --> 00:11:38,846
Chef, there is no need
to do all this.

144
00:11:38,933 --> 00:11:40,766
He will do something
and get caught of his own accord.

145
00:11:44,493 --> 00:11:46,806
Sorry, Chef, I-I will go.

146
00:12:07,076 --> 00:12:08,166
Give it to me.
- Yeah.

147
00:12:11,406 --> 00:12:12,486
Everything was good.

148
00:12:13,726 --> 00:12:15,686
Shruthi.
- Yes, Mom.

149
00:12:16,486 --> 00:12:19,926
Give me two minutes.
I will talk to Joji and come.

150
00:12:21,159 --> 00:12:24,719
Why, Mom? You stay here.
Don't do unnecessary things.

151
00:12:25,726 --> 00:12:28,943
After your dad passed away,
I have lived my life only for you.

152
00:12:29,166 --> 00:12:31,543
I am not asking you.
I am telling you.

153
00:12:32,053 --> 00:12:34,486
Mom..

154
00:12:45,206 --> 00:12:46,326
Sorry, Joji.

155
00:12:46,851 --> 00:12:48,971
We had a fight
in the room last night.

156
00:12:49,563 --> 00:12:52,853
I am the one who usually
starts the fight.

157
00:12:53,446 --> 00:12:57,926
But yesterday, I was getting
scolded by them for a change.

158
00:13:00,490 --> 00:13:01,450
Sorry.

159
00:13:02,284 --> 00:13:06,657
I put you in an uncomfortable
situation yesterday, right?

160
00:13:09,081 --> 00:13:11,710
Nothing like that, dear.
- No.

161
00:13:12,085 --> 00:13:13,245
I know.

162
00:13:14,254 --> 00:13:17,310
You would have felt bad, right?
- Leave it, Padma.

163
00:13:19,206 --> 00:13:20,886
I too want to apologise to you.

164
00:13:23,126 --> 00:13:26,166
It is because of me that there is
so much problem in your family.

165
00:13:26,806 --> 00:13:28,566
That is not a problem.
I'll deal with it.

166
00:13:28,843 --> 00:13:30,966
I also want to stay
for a few more days.

167
00:13:32,176 --> 00:13:34,166
But, I can't.

168
00:13:36,566 --> 00:13:39,846
But, the days I was with you..

169
00:13:40,476 --> 00:13:43,206
Like the way
you remembered my dress code..

170
00:13:43,943 --> 00:13:47,766
I want you to always
be in my memories.

171
00:13:49,086 --> 00:13:53,326
Before you came,
I had no motive in my life.

172
00:13:53,613 --> 00:13:58,046
But, after this, I will
think that you are with me.

173
00:13:58,606 --> 00:14:00,406
With that, I can spend
the rest of my life.

174
00:14:02,726 --> 00:14:06,766
Will anyone get a chance
to relive their past life?

175
00:14:08,606 --> 00:14:11,326
I don't know. But, I got it.

176
00:14:13,166 --> 00:14:16,110
I am very happy.
- Okay, Joji.

177
00:14:17,019 --> 00:14:20,203
If you feel like it, call me.
- Sure.

178
00:14:20,386 --> 00:14:22,626
If that is all,
we will come together again.

179
00:14:23,526 --> 00:14:25,526
We will definitely meet.
- Sure.

180
00:14:27,110 --> 00:14:28,043
Mom.

181
00:14:32,707 --> 00:14:35,677
It's okay, dear.
They are waiting for you.

182
00:14:35,874 --> 00:14:38,726
You leave.
- Okay, Joji.

183
00:14:39,172 --> 00:14:41,492
We will meet again. Bye.

184
00:14:43,046 --> 00:14:43,966
Bye.

185
00:15:58,219 --> 00:15:59,379
What are you saying?

186
00:16:00,286 --> 00:16:02,610
How can I find someone
at the last minute?

187
00:16:02,743 --> 00:16:04,246
I've given it to that room.

188
00:16:04,643 --> 00:16:05,846
In this room..

189
00:16:12,806 --> 00:16:15,086
I found one.
Hang up the phone.

190
00:16:19,105 --> 00:16:21,581
Hey, do you know
how to play the guitar?

191
00:16:22,246 --> 00:16:23,326
Guitar?

192
00:16:24,143 --> 00:16:26,646
I want to play it.
But, I don't know how to play it.

193
00:16:27,010 --> 00:16:29,043
Is that it?
Okay, come with me.

194
00:16:29,646 --> 00:16:30,766
I will give you a guitar.

195
00:16:31,110 --> 00:16:33,806
Just act as if you are playing it.

196
00:16:34,966 --> 00:16:36,286
What if someone finds out?

197
00:16:36,910 --> 00:16:38,243
I will take care of it. You come.

198
00:16:40,446 --> 00:16:43,646
You will take care of it. You know
how to sing and you'll rock it.

199
00:16:44,246 --> 00:16:47,406
But, when I don't know how
to play it, I'll be ashamed, right?

200
00:16:48,410 --> 00:16:49,966
I will take care of all that.

201
00:16:50,428 --> 00:16:52,151
There will be music
in the background.

202
00:16:52,646 --> 00:16:54,126
Just play it.

203
00:16:55,806 --> 00:16:59,206
If the music stops, then
I will play it like a mad man.

204
00:17:02,566 --> 00:17:04,406
Will you give me a signal
before the music stops?

205
00:17:05,310 --> 00:17:07,376
Oh, are you okay with it then?

206
00:17:08,076 --> 00:17:09,343
I'm okay, why?

207
00:17:09,698 --> 00:17:11,458
Why did you say okay so quickly?

208
00:17:12,126 --> 00:17:14,526
Hey, do I have to come or not?

209
00:17:15,793 --> 00:17:17,446
I was just kidding.

210
00:17:20,166 --> 00:17:22,806
But, you won't make
a fool out of me, right?

211
00:17:25,881 --> 00:17:27,361
Hey, Kumudha,
why are you laughing?

212
00:17:27,747 --> 00:17:29,206
I am coming because I trust you.

213
00:17:29,926 --> 00:17:31,886
No old traps, right?

214
00:17:32,443 --> 00:17:33,806
You come, let's see.

215
00:17:33,886 --> 00:17:36,046
Is there any payment?
- Yes. A lot.

216
00:17:36,113 --> 00:17:39,766
If you'd told me sooner, I wouldn't
have asked so many questions.

217
00:19:06,366 --> 00:19:08,726
It was good.
- Is it?

218
00:19:08,843 --> 00:19:11,206
I have been playing
guitar for a year.

219
00:19:11,606 --> 00:19:14,206
You did very well.
It was very professional. - Thanks.

220
00:19:14,273 --> 00:19:15,776
Was it professional?
Oh, wow..

221
00:19:15,824 --> 00:19:18,119
Whenever I play, I play
as if it's my first time.

222
00:19:18,246 --> 00:19:20,926
Who are you talking to?
- Aishu, she is a fan of mine.

223
00:19:21,773 --> 00:19:22,686
Sister.

224
00:19:34,543 --> 00:19:35,886
How come you're here?

225
00:19:37,095 --> 00:19:39,705
Even I know where I'll be.

226
00:19:39,890 --> 00:19:43,250
How did you come here?
- I am following you closely.

227
00:19:44,102 --> 00:19:47,385
I have seen you at an event before,
without your knowledge.

228
00:19:48,315 --> 00:19:50,105
You could have come
and talked to me.

229
00:19:50,566 --> 00:19:54,210
I came to talk to you.
But, you were in a hurry.

230
00:19:54,486 --> 00:19:57,046
So, I didn't want to stop you.

231
00:20:00,446 --> 00:20:02,126
How are you?
Is everything fine?

232
00:20:02,643 --> 00:20:04,486
I am fine.
How are you?

233
00:20:05,476 --> 00:20:08,246
How is Dad?
Is he still angry with me?

234
00:20:09,003 --> 00:20:09,886
Then?

235
00:20:11,366 --> 00:20:14,846
How could he not be angry?

236
00:20:16,301 --> 00:20:17,981
He carries a lot of anger.

237
00:20:18,345 --> 00:20:22,508
Even though I am angry
with him, I want to see him.

238
00:20:23,926 --> 00:20:25,846
He will be home.
Will you come?

239
00:20:26,686 --> 00:20:27,686
Oh, no.

240
00:20:27,963 --> 00:20:31,410
If I think of coming
to our house in this situation,

241
00:20:31,526 --> 00:20:34,766
I feel like I am entering
a haunted house. I'm so scared.

242
00:20:35,686 --> 00:20:38,043
It's okay, come and eat.

243
00:20:38,246 --> 00:20:39,776
I am a ghost who cooks well.

244
00:20:43,810 --> 00:20:44,686
Hey.

245
00:20:46,086 --> 00:20:48,246
She is my sister.
- Sister?

246
00:20:49,584 --> 00:20:51,064
Mr. Nedumaran has two daughters?

247
00:20:53,286 --> 00:20:55,326
Stop staring
and take a photo of us.

248
00:20:56,766 --> 00:20:57,606
Here.

249
00:21:03,646 --> 00:21:06,246
Smile, you two look alike.

250
00:21:08,810 --> 00:21:11,243
Take a nice photo, not like
your fake guitar pose from before.

251
00:21:11,343 --> 00:21:12,915
Okay?
- What are you saying?

252
00:21:12,963 --> 00:21:15,686
Was it acting?
- Yes..

253
00:21:16,006 --> 00:21:17,326
He was acting.
- Sorry..

254
00:21:25,704 --> 00:21:26,541
Oh, no.

255
00:21:26,678 --> 00:21:28,334
How long will you take?
- He keeps calling.

256
00:21:28,383 --> 00:21:30,126
Oh, no, I attended the call.

257
00:21:32,710 --> 00:21:33,603
'Hey..'

258
00:21:34,170 --> 00:21:36,033
'What the hell?'
- Sir.

259
00:21:38,646 --> 00:21:40,886
'Aishu..'

260
00:21:41,646 --> 00:21:43,446
Hi, sir.

261
00:21:43,503 --> 00:21:46,326
'What the hell are you doing there?'
- What happened? - What happened?

262
00:21:48,246 --> 00:21:50,143
Hey, hello..

263
00:21:50,846 --> 00:21:53,076
What is it?
- Nothing..

264
00:21:53,810 --> 00:21:55,676
Shall we take a selfie?
- Yes, let's take one.
